  "title": "Part-time Operations Executive (Fashion Industry)",
  "description": "<p>📦<strong> Start ASAP</strong><br /><strong>📦 Training Provided</strong><br /><strong>📦 Fresh Grad Welcome</strong><br /><br /><strong>💰 Salary:</strong> $10/hour<br /><br /><strong>📍Working Location: </strong>Serangoon<br /><br /><strong>🕘Working Hours:</strong><br />Monday - Friday<br />9:00 - 18:00 | 13:00 - 18:00</p><p>⚠️ <strong>Minimum Commitment:</strong><br />2-3 working days per week (Monday Mandatory)<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Day-to-day operations (including but not limited to packing of parcels)</li><li>Dispatch of international orders</li><li>Liaising with courier partners</li><li>Stock take/arrangement of racks</li><li>Stocking up for retail store</li><li>Processing of walk-ins/exchanges and returns</li><li>Upholding team efficiency and ensuring operations run smoothly within the timeline</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Proficient in English</li><li>Experience in e-commerce operations/similar is preferred</li><li>Comfortable working in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Able to commit a minimum of 6 months</li></ul><p>📩 Interested candidates may send their resumes to <strong>hr@lovet.sg</strong><br /><em>*Shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p>",
